WEBVTT

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:03.930
[VOICE OVER] In this module, you have learned 
about credit card data and some of the ways that 

00:00:03.931 --> 00:00:06.345
cybercriminals try to gain access to that information. 

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:11.155
Keeping credit card data safe is often about the actions 
that you do or do not take. 

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:16.200
We also covered a variety of best practices related 
to the protection of credit card information. 

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:22.920
Remember, protecting credit card data is up to you, 
so make sure that you stop, look, and think before 

00:00:22.921 --> 00:00:24.300
you take any type of action. 

00:00:24.450 --> 00:00:27.560
